lines.text: when they thightly strap me in
give me lethal injection
just a few moments to live
no remorse for what i did
was for the betterment of man
i gave the utmost sacrfice
before more damage could be done i took his life
there was a split second of silence
when the dart punctured the skin
beady eyes roll back in head
body dropped under poisin
they could incapaciate me
but could not erease my sneer
i heard a thousand people screaming
while three billion otther cheered
he was gone and i will soon be
execuded by the state
all appeals would be invain
i was not criminally insane
in fact i was- found to be
an otherwise caring and respectable member
of society
a minor threat exept for that one man i killed
as the sedantives takes effect
i just smile and close my eyes
there's a priest kneeling next to me
he ask me if i realize
i was going straight to- hell
and he thougt that i should know
that the man i killed replacement
planned this whole scenario
what i did had no significance at all
